{"tid":2157375,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"反對派號召和平示威","createTime":"2020-08-15T03:59:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T04:00:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fac3aa8111d2efb13bf9e6ce503a4db51cdb24a1","tid":2157375,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T03:59:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200815/TE2FLAM3JVHD3IBYPVNTAWQMBY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200815%2FTE2FLAM3JVHD3IBYPVNTAWQMBY%2F&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8RFNIXSBonesC3SPsSCGYVE%3D&h=abbf345e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200815%2FTE2FLAM3JVHD3IBYPVNTAWQMBY%2F&h=32c26f64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200815/TE2FLAM3JVHD3IBYPVNTAWQMBY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n反對派號召和平示威<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/627m1vQ8M1f_f8EtoBLDepj-fsM=/1779x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/J7BGHEURBJCJJCDO7FBB3WZ6UQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F627m1vQ8M1f_f8EtoBLDepj-fsM%3D%2F1779x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJ7BGHEURBJCJJCDO7FBB3WZ6UQ.jpg&h=b1d55d64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■有少女手持鮮花在明斯克參與示威。<br />\n<br />\n流亡立陶宛的白俄羅斯前反對派總統候選人季哈諾夫斯卡婭，昨日在影片分享網站上載影片，呼籲支持網上聯署要求重新點票之餘，號召支持者本周末在全國「和平示威」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n默克爾促制裁白俄<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。她昨日在YouTube呼籲民眾本周末在全國所有城市和平示威。她說：「白俄羅斯人永不希望再活於前政府治下。大多數人都不相信他（盧卡申科）勝出。」她續說：「我呼籲全國所有城市的市長，在8月15及16日在各地籌辦大型和平集會。」她又呼籲支持者支持網上聯署要求重新點票：「六個月前，沒有人會相信白俄斯人可團結起來向舊政府說『不』。但現在發生了。政府將民眾上街和平集會變成血淋淋的屠殺。」。。。。。。。。。。。。。。歐盟委員會主席馮德萊恩昨日表態，支持制裁「那些違反民主價值或侵犯人權」的白俄羅斯官員；至少九個歐盟國家領袖，包括德國總理默克爾支持制裁白俄羅斯。<br />\n<br />\n路透社/法新社"},{"pid":"50810f2287440d3616c89757645da53e0ad1fdcc","tid":2157375,"uid":189157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T04:00:50.000Z","msg":"左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對抗極權暴政只有革命先係唯一出路"}]}